Magnetic Faith
Discworld ritual help
Magnetic Faith

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Magnetic Faith -- fills an item with a holy magneticism.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Magnetic Faith infuses an object with the strength of your faith. You need 
a holy symbol and a prayer book to perform this ritual. This infusion means
that, if mislaid, the object is inclined to stick to whoever may then pick
it up for a period of time.
.EP
